**Tattling** | Attribute
__Basics__
Each night, a Tattling player may check a player's. The result will be sent to a random player with an investigative role. The player will receive the name of the investigated player and their role.

__Formalized__
End Night:
  • Process:
    ‣ Target @(Cat:Investigative)->RandomPlayer
    ‣ Role Investigate @Selection (SD)
  • Evaluate:
    ‣ Reveal `@Selection is @Result2` to @Target
